{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/[lang]/layout,_N_T_/[lang]/about/layout,_N_T_/[lang]/about/page,_N_T_/en/about"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/$d$lang/about/__PAGE__","/$d$lang/about","/$d$lang","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html class=\"open_sans_573b549b-module__BY3tqa__variable h-full antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/cf514f5d0007dafa-s.p.1wc2mf9hp9pav.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-5.png\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/safety-Link-Team-.png\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-1.png\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/305zfmpkz2n9r.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/3z5q_p4msz2ha.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/15orcrkp-_9ct.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2nykiepra7i1k.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07u_h6i539_wj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-3gtektv3c62t6.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1-z_8zqv2wo99.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>SafetyLink | Legally Defensible Safety Compliance</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"The Gold Standard in Legally Defensible Safety that Protects Your People and Your Business.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><html lang=\"en\"><header class=\"bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/en\"><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-5.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-10 w-auto\"/></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en\">Home</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/solutions\">Solutions</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Request Demo</a><a class=\"text-[#686868] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Login</a><a class=\"text-xs text-navy font-semibold bg-[#eef3ff] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/es\">ES</a></nav><button class=\"lg:hidden text-navy p-2\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-navy text-white py-20 px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-primary text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold mb-4\">About Us</p><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4\">The Experts Behind the Only Legally Defensible Safety Platform</h1><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Led by former OSHA leadership and backed by top labor law experts, SafetyLink delivers compliance solutions you can trust with confidence.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6\">Founded by Safety Leaders, Guided by OSHA Experts</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] leading-relaxed mb-6\">With over two decades of safety leadership experience, SafetyLink was founded with a bold mission: to close the gap between regulatory compliance and real-world workplace protection. Built on a vision of legally defensible safety solutions, SafetyLink is transforming how organizations approach OSHA compliance.</p><p class=\"text-navy font-semibold mb-6\">Our advisory board includes Edwin Foulke Jr., former Assistant Secretary of Labor for OSHA, and Bert Brennan, renowned labor law expert. Their combined 60+ years of OSHA leadership ensures our platform meets the highest standards of regulatory compliance.</p><p class=\"text-[#666] leading-relaxed\">Unlike generic safety software, SafetyLink combines OSHA-authorized expertise with cutting-edge technology. Our legally defensible platform provides bilingual support and industry-specific solutions backed by decades of regulatory leadership.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><img src=\"/images/safety-Link-Team-.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink Team\" class=\"rounded-2xl shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] w-full\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 0%, rgb(244, 243, 242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4\">Our Mission &amp; Vision</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-lg\">Driving the future of workplace safety through expert-led compliance solutions</p></div><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">🎯</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3\">Our Mission</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">To protect workers and businesses by delivering legally defensible, OSHA-authorized compliance solutions that go beyond check-the-box requirements to create genuinely safe workplaces.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">👁️</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3\">Our Vision</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">To transform safety compliance from a burden into confidence, empowering organizations across every industry to protect their workforce with solutions they can trust completely.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4\">Our Core Values</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-lg\">The principles that guide everything we do at SafetyLink</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-3\">🛡️</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Integrity &amp; Trust</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">We build solutions with unwavering integrity, ensuring every compliance tool and program we deliver can be trusted completely.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-3\">❤️</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Worker Protection First</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Every decision we make prioritizes the safety and wellbeing of workers, because protecting people is our highest responsibility.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-3\">📋</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Compliance Through Expertise</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Our OSHA-authorized leadership ensures that every solution we provide meets the highest standards of regulatory compliance.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-3\">💡</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Innovation in Training &amp; Technology</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">We continuously innovate to make safety training more effective, accessible, and engaging for diverse workforces.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 0%, rgb(244, 243, 242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4\">Advisory Board</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-lg\">Industry leaders and regulatory experts who guide SafetyLink&#x27;s mission</p></div><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] flex gap-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0\">EF</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy\">Edwin Foulke Jr.</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm font-semibold mb-1\">Former Assistant Secretary of Labor for OSHA</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">OSHA Leadership</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Edwin served as the Assistant Secretary of Labor for OSHA under President George W. Bush. His extensive experience in workplace safety regulation and enforcement brings unparalleled expertise to SafetyLink&#x27;s compliance solutions.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] flex gap-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0\">BB</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy\">Bert Brennan</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm font-semibold mb-1\">Senior Labor Law Partner</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Labor Law</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">A renowned labor law expert with over 30 years of experience representing employers in OSHA matters. Bert&#x27;s deep understanding of regulatory compliance helps ensure SafetyLink&#x27;s legal defensibility.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] flex gap-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0\">DS</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy\">Dr. Sarah Chen</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm font-semibold mb-1\">Occupational Health Specialist</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Health &amp; Safety</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Leading occupational health researcher with expertise in workplace safety metrics and injury prevention. Her insights drive SafetyLink&#x27;s evidence-based approach to safety program development.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] flex gap-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0\">MR</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-navy\">Michael Rodriguez</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm font-semibold mb-1\">Technology Innovation Advisor</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Safety Technology</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Former CTO of leading safety technology companies with expertise in compliance software and training platforms. Michael guides SafetyLink&#x27;s technological innovation and user experience.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6 bg-navy text-center text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Discover how our team makes compliance defensible.</h2><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-lg mb-10\">Experience the difference that OSHA-authorized expertise and proven leadership can make for your organization&#x27;s safety compliance.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap\"><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Request A Demo</a><a class=\"inline-block bg-transparent text-white border-2 border-white px-10 py-4 rounded-[10px] font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-white hover:text-navy transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Request A Consult</a></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10\"><div><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-1.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-8 w-auto mb-4\"/><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">The only legally defensible safety compliance platform backed by OSHA leadership and top labor law experts. Protecting workforces with bilingual training, audits, and compliance solutions.</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 italic\">SafetyLink is not affiliated with or endorsed by OSHA. Advisory support provided by former OSHA leadership.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/solutions\">Solutions</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/services\">Services</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Login</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Compliance &amp; Trust</h4><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2\"><p>Safety Link, LLC</p><p>111 Congress Ave, Suite 500</p><p>Austin, Texas 78701</p><p class=\"pt-2\">888-373-7822</p><p>833-780-0728</p><p>compliance@safetylink.ai</p><div class=\"flex gap-1 items-center pt-2 text-xs text-primary\"><span>✓</span> OSHA Authorized Trainers</div><div class=\"flex gap-1 items-center text-xs text-primary\"><span>✓</span> SOC 2 Compliant</div></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-gray-400\"><p>© 2026 SafetyLink. All rights reserved. Legally defensible safety compliance solutions.</p><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/terms-of-service\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/accessibility\">Accessibility</a></div></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--></html><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3z5q_p4msz2ha.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]